1
00:01:26,770 --> 00:01:30,770
=My Dear Guardian=

2
00:01:31,340 --> 00:01:34,120
=Episode 36=

3
00:01:42,630 --> 00:01:44,280
He got high on anaesthesia.

4
00:01:44,360 --> 00:01:45,789
He is talking nonsense.

5
00:01:45,979 --> 00:01:48,688
He is talking nonsense.
But you feel happy after hearing it.

6
00:01:49,101 --> 00:01:50,969
Who's talking nonsense?

7
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:54,442
I'm Sailor Moon.

8
00:01:54,522 --> 00:01:56,688
In the name of the Moon, I'll punish you!

9
00:01:57,178 --> 00:01:59,775
Oh, my.
Isn't this Sailor Moon's catchphrase?

10
00:01:59,864 --> 00:02:03,656
I can't believe I'm hearing this
from a special forces soldier.

11
00:02:03,736 --> 00:02:04,786
Did you teach him that?

12
00:02:05,490 --> 00:02:06,417
No. I...

13
00:02:06,497 --> 00:02:07,549
No.

14
00:02:08,086 --> 00:02:13,231
Sailor Moon is a couple gift from her.

15
00:02:13,719 --> 00:02:14,880
Liang Mu Ze.

16
00:02:14,961 --> 00:02:17,135
A set of Sailor Moon bed sheet.

17
00:02:17,215 --> 00:02:18,957
Liang Mu Ze, keep quiet.

18
00:02:19,037 --> 00:02:20,354
Bed sheet?

19
00:02:21,631 --> 00:02:23,825
-No.
-You don't need to explain it.

20
00:02:23,905 --> 00:02:24,985
Your dad is here.

21
00:02:25,110 --> 00:02:26,298
He's waiting at the door.

22
00:02:28,312 --> 00:02:30,287
What are you doing? Just go.

23
00:02:31,487 --> 00:02:32,802
Check his body temperature.

24
00:02:32,882 --> 00:02:34,446
His face was hot just now.

25
00:02:35,342 --> 00:02:36,217
Xia Chu.

26
00:02:37,518 --> 00:02:38,905
Xia Chu.

27
00:02:39,799 --> 00:02:40,982
Xia Chu.

28
00:02:42,892 --> 00:02:44,049
I love you.

29
00:02:44,329 --> 00:02:45,514
Stop it. Captain Liang.

30
00:02:45,594 --> 00:02:47,868
Let me check your body temperature.

31
00:03:18,161 --> 00:03:20,166
Where did you come from?

32
00:03:20,660 --> 00:03:22,996
I came from my mother's womb.

33
00:03:27,632 --> 00:03:29,165
Why did you come here?

34
00:03:31,031 --> 00:03:32,706
What do you think?

35
00:03:35,932 --> 00:03:38,654
After receiving the call from your unit,
I was frightened.

36
00:03:38,914 --> 00:03:41,912
So I asked your grandpa to contact
the leader at your war zone.

37
00:03:41,992 --> 00:03:45,437
When I heard that you're safe
and have completed the exercise,

38
00:03:45,942 --> 00:03:47,528
I came to see you immediately.

39
00:03:49,772 --> 00:03:52,004
You asked Grandpa for help?

40
00:03:53,122 --> 00:03:54,573
It's all because of you.

41
00:03:55,332 --> 00:03:57,554
I can do everything for you.

42
00:04:03,350 --> 00:04:04,307
So...

43
00:04:04,621 --> 00:04:05,839
Does Mum know about it?

44
00:04:05,919 --> 00:04:07,331
I dare not tell her.

45
00:04:08,793 --> 00:04:10,874
Although I normally do things slowly,

46
00:04:10,954 --> 00:04:13,586
when a big problem occurs,
I am very clear-headed.

47
00:04:15,372 --> 00:04:17,251
I've informed your grandpa.

48
00:04:17,936 --> 00:04:19,845
So she won't know about this.

49
00:04:19,925 --> 00:04:21,255
Don't worry.

50
00:04:28,832 --> 00:04:30,452
I'm sorry, Dad.

51
00:04:35,132 --> 00:04:36,942
You have your own life.

52
00:04:37,032 --> 00:04:40,352
I can't make decisions for you.

53
00:04:41,556 --> 00:04:45,642
But you have to think carefully about it.

54
00:04:47,012 --> 00:04:48,392
I've thought about it.

55
00:04:49,952 --> 00:04:51,202
However...

56
00:04:52,352 --> 00:04:53,502
However?

57
00:04:56,142 --> 00:05:00,924
If I don't become a great doctor...

58
00:05:01,854 --> 00:05:03,584
who makes history,

59
00:05:05,162 --> 00:05:06,397
will you be disappointed?

60
00:05:22,723 --> 00:05:26,537
I have overcome
many difficulties in life.

61
00:05:27,756 --> 00:05:28,953
So many.

62
00:05:30,672 --> 00:05:31,928
To me,

63
00:05:33,341 --> 00:05:36,108
I only have one most important
masterpiece.

64
00:05:37,062 --> 00:05:38,139
And that is you.

65
00:05:40,912 --> 00:05:44,575
So since the day you were born,

66
00:05:45,460 --> 00:05:47,733
no matter what job you do,

67
00:05:47,813 --> 00:05:50,053
be it a success or failure,

68
00:05:50,753 --> 00:05:53,495
my answer remains the same.

69
00:06:01,982 --> 00:06:05,330
I want to join Liang Mu Ze
at his outpost.

70
00:06:16,142 --> 00:06:17,826
Life is short.

71
00:06:18,662 --> 00:06:21,137
I hope you will be happy.

72
00:06:21,982 --> 00:06:23,659
Life can be long too.

73
00:06:24,076 --> 00:06:26,753
So you must find carefully...

74
00:06:27,522 --> 00:06:30,114
the one who will be your life partner.

75
00:06:30,782 --> 00:06:33,420
But don't worry about making mistakes.

76
00:06:34,502 --> 00:06:36,731
Dad and Mum will always be with you.

77
00:06:37,207 --> 00:06:38,221
Got it?

78
00:06:40,782 --> 00:06:41,886
Yes.

79
00:06:44,582 --> 00:06:45,757
Thank you, Dad.

80
00:06:46,521 --> 00:06:48,565
I will be very happy.

81
00:06:56,062 --> 00:07:00,592
The moon is lingering...

82
00:07:07,462 --> 00:07:09,012
-Brigade Commander.
-Don't sit up.

83
00:07:09,102 --> 00:07:10,122
Just lie down.

84
00:07:14,382 --> 00:07:15,549
Are you okay?

85
00:07:16,046 --> 00:07:16,995
I'm okay.

86
00:07:17,636 --> 00:07:18,956
I had some allergies.

87
00:07:19,036 --> 00:07:20,039
I'm fine now.

88
00:07:21,222 --> 00:07:22,532
What about you?

89
00:07:22,622 --> 00:07:24,807
I'm fine. I just had a few stitches.

90
00:07:25,462 --> 00:07:26,543
Good to hear that.

91
00:07:28,582 --> 00:07:29,798
Actually...

92
00:07:31,102 --> 00:07:34,904
the command post told me
that the foreigner who got caught...

93
00:07:35,420 --> 00:07:36,628
mentioned about Tian Yong.

94
00:07:42,782 --> 00:07:45,650
This is the photo given by the police.

95
00:07:45,730 --> 00:07:49,092
It's confirmed that he is the commander.

96
00:07:55,705 --> 00:07:56,612
What's the matter?

97
00:07:57,075 --> 00:07:58,014
Do you know him?

98
00:07:58,792 --> 00:08:01,090
His name is Zhuo Ran.

99
00:08:02,222 --> 00:08:03,671
He's Xia Chu's first love.

100
00:08:04,105 --> 00:08:05,796
He was missing since 18 years old.

101
00:08:05,876 --> 00:08:07,536
He just came back
to the country this year.

102
00:08:07,616 --> 00:08:08,487
You're right.

103
00:08:09,702 --> 00:08:11,315
When he was missing,

104
00:08:11,562 --> 00:08:13,542
he was using another identity.

105
00:08:14,098 --> 00:08:16,423
He was in the military
and have been at war.

106
00:08:17,095 --> 00:08:19,960
He's the most valuable mercenary
in the world right now.

107
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:22,381
One of the representatives
in the foreign armed forces...

108
00:08:22,941 --> 00:08:24,307
is a former comrade in arms.

109
00:08:24,810 --> 00:08:26,650
What is his other name?

110
00:08:27,862 --> 00:08:28,994
Pei Yu.

111
00:08:30,481 --> 00:08:32,598
You're not the first one
who said that I'm lucky.

112
00:08:32,678 --> 00:08:33,830
Who else?

113
00:08:34,814 --> 00:08:36,505
He was not a comrade in arms.

114
00:08:36,585 --> 00:08:37,890
Before you,

115
00:08:38,248 --> 00:08:39,667
he was my only failure.

116
00:08:46,602 --> 00:08:48,781
Who is this guy?

117
00:08:53,662 --> 00:08:54,677
Pei Yu.

118
00:09:03,152 --> 00:09:04,639
The higher-ups gave order...

119
00:09:05,418 --> 00:09:08,520
to have liaison between the police
and the military for a full search.

120
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:09,821
Is there any news?

121
00:09:09,901 --> 00:09:10,978
As of now,

122
00:09:11,411 --> 00:09:14,145
we are stepping up the search.

123
00:09:15,262 --> 00:09:18,238
Your mission is to focus on recovery.

124
00:09:32,432 --> 00:09:34,183
Miss Mi Gu, I have received
the amended proposal.

125
00:09:34,263 --> 00:09:36,185
What shall we do next?

126
00:09:36,265 --> 00:09:38,170
-Mi Gu.
-Do you have 10 thousand RMB?

127
00:09:38,250 --> 00:09:39,552
I'm doing a business with my friends.

128
00:09:39,632 --> 00:09:41,345
I still need some money
to join the partnership.

129
00:09:41,425 --> 00:09:43,865
You must help your brother.

130
00:09:43,945 --> 00:09:45,743
Call him before weekend.

131
00:09:45,823 --> 00:09:48,818
Help him to achieve his dream
to start a business.

132
00:09:48,898 --> 00:09:50,628
Miss Mi Gu, are you feeling better?

133
00:09:50,708 --> 00:09:51,704
Mi Gu.

134
00:09:51,784 --> 00:09:53,653
I found someone else
to manage your programme.

135
00:09:53,733 --> 00:09:54,961
You take a rest at home.

136
00:10:22,132 --> 00:10:23,208
I'm warning you.

137
00:10:23,288 --> 00:10:24,768
Don't call me again!

138
00:10:25,762 --> 00:10:26,802
Mi Gu.

139
00:10:30,342 --> 00:10:31,362
Zhuo Ran?

140
00:10:36,597 --> 00:10:37,492
Is that you?

141
00:10:37,582 --> 00:10:39,867
Yes, it's me.

142
00:10:56,102 --> 00:10:58,161
Did anyone follow you here?

143
00:10:59,925 --> 00:11:01,015
No.

144
00:11:02,023 --> 00:11:06,098
I have deleted
the address that you sent to me.

145
00:11:06,178 --> 00:11:07,655
I've applied a long leave.

146
00:11:14,992 --> 00:11:16,595
May I know the reason?

147
00:11:30,422 --> 00:11:31,867
Let's go to the hospital.

148
00:13:51,952 --> 00:13:54,125
Zhuo Ran.

149
00:13:58,742 --> 00:13:59,824
Zhuo Ran.

150
00:14:28,142 --> 00:14:29,162
I'm cold.

151
00:14:35,142 --> 00:14:36,042
I'm cold.

152
00:14:37,932 --> 00:14:38,832
So cold.

153
00:14:39,582 --> 00:14:40,882
I'm cold.

154
00:14:52,811 --> 00:14:58,571
♪I'd like to find out♪

155
00:14:59,072 --> 00:15:04,092
♪If my mask of foolishness♪

156
00:15:05,262 --> 00:15:11,312
♪Could deceive you♪

157
00:15:11,682 --> 00:15:15,672
♪I'm putting on my best performance♪

158
00:15:15,752 --> 00:15:16,682
I'm cold.

159
00:15:23,422 --> 00:15:24,609
Mum.

160
00:15:28,542 --> 00:15:30,812
Why did you only take my brother with you?

161
00:15:33,102 --> 00:15:34,452
You're unfair.

162
00:15:36,782 --> 00:15:38,412
Are you going to abandon me?

163
00:15:41,272 --> 00:15:42,692
Don't leave me.

164
00:15:43,782 --> 00:15:45,012
Don't leave me.

165
00:15:46,422 --> 00:15:47,482
Don't go.

166
00:15:48,382 --> 00:15:49,562
Don't leave me here.

167
00:15:57,022 --> 00:15:58,362
I won't go.

168
00:16:02,672 --> 00:16:04,652
I won't leave you here.

169
00:16:14,502 --> 00:16:16,162
I won't leave you here.

170
00:16:25,182 --> 00:16:28,322
The Training Unit and Public Security
Bureau has confirmed his identity.

171
00:16:29,062 --> 00:16:30,185
According to their analysis,

172
00:16:30,658 --> 00:16:33,647
it's highly possible
that he came back to the city.

173
00:16:34,061 --> 00:16:36,585
They have asked us
to do a thorough investigation.

174
00:16:36,665 --> 00:16:38,808
Find out his whereabouts
as soon as possible.

175
00:16:38,888 --> 00:16:39,963
Yes, sir.

176
00:16:40,862 --> 00:16:42,372
Unit One. Continue to track Tian Yong.

177
00:16:42,462 --> 00:16:43,557
Unit Two, follow me.

178
00:16:43,637 --> 00:16:44,676
Yes, sir.

179
00:16:48,952 --> 00:16:49,991
Xia Chu.

180
00:16:50,071 --> 00:16:51,228
Xia Chu.

181
00:16:51,942 --> 00:16:53,463
Xia Chu, there is a problem.

182
00:16:53,543 --> 00:16:56,035
Liang Mu Ze's condition is not good.
Go have a look.

183
00:17:11,272 --> 00:17:12,947
Sir. How is he now?

184
00:17:13,027 --> 00:17:14,571
He has high fever.

185
00:17:14,651 --> 00:17:17,252
He also has indirect muscle spasms.

186
00:17:17,332 --> 00:17:18,508
From my initial findings,

187
00:17:18,886 --> 00:17:20,285
his wound is infected.

188
00:17:23,832 --> 00:17:24,781
Infected?

189
00:17:25,772 --> 00:17:27,317
I've taken his blood sample.

190
00:17:27,397 --> 00:17:29,077
I will take it to the hospital
for testing.

191
00:17:42,102 --> 00:17:44,361
Xia Chu. Don't stand there. Hurry up.

192
00:17:44,982 --> 00:17:46,176
Xia Chu.

193
00:17:46,770 --> 00:17:47,940
What?

194
00:17:48,020 --> 00:17:49,591
Send him back to the hospital.

195
00:17:49,939 --> 00:17:51,657
The condition here is not ideal.

196
00:17:51,737 --> 00:17:52,753
Yes.

197
00:17:52,833 --> 00:17:54,368
Let's do it together.

198
00:18:01,022 --> 00:18:02,393
Don't worry, Commander Dong.

199
00:18:02,473 --> 00:18:04,823
I will report Captain Liang's condition
to you.

200
00:18:04,903 --> 00:18:06,244
Thank you, Xia Chu.

201
00:18:07,204 --> 00:18:08,486
Dad, I'll get going.

202
00:18:08,566 --> 00:18:09,629
Go.

203
00:18:15,132 --> 00:18:16,416
Be careful.

204
00:19:11,582 --> 00:19:13,375
According to the test results,

205
00:19:13,455 --> 00:19:15,794
it should be
Acinetobacter Baumannii infection.

206
00:19:15,874 --> 00:19:18,602
We have sent Liang Mu Ze
to the emergency room.

207
00:19:18,682 --> 00:19:21,998
After several consultations,
we put on high dosage of sulbactam...

208
00:19:22,078 --> 00:19:23,875
and combined with tigecycline.

209
00:19:23,955 --> 00:19:26,521
We hope it can control
the bacteria in his body.

210
00:19:28,902 --> 00:19:30,473
Is it controlled?

211
00:19:32,022 --> 00:19:33,931
We are unable to confirm that now.

212
00:19:34,545 --> 00:19:36,241
After some time,

213
00:19:36,710 --> 00:19:39,710
we will do an analysis
of the bacteria in his body.

214
00:19:39,790 --> 00:19:40,910
Only then,

215
00:19:41,364 --> 00:19:43,207
will we know if the medicine is effective.

216
00:19:43,912 --> 00:19:45,072
So...

217
00:19:46,096 --> 00:19:47,360
If it is not effective,

218
00:19:48,312 --> 00:19:49,415
what will happen?

219
00:19:50,742 --> 00:19:52,663
We have prepared several plans.

220
00:19:52,743 --> 00:19:55,903
If this doesn't work,
we will try another plan.

221
00:20:00,262 --> 00:20:01,988
He should have changed jobs.

222
00:20:02,578 --> 00:20:04,837
If he hadn't joined the exercise,
he wouldn't be injured.

223
00:20:04,917 --> 00:20:06,371
His wound wouldn't have been infected too.

224
00:20:06,451 --> 00:20:07,642
Enough.

225
00:20:07,722 --> 00:20:08,888
You don't have to say it.

226
00:20:10,102 --> 00:20:11,092
Sir.

227
00:20:12,238 --> 00:20:13,346
Madam.

228
00:20:13,828 --> 00:20:15,052
I'm sorry.

229
00:20:16,262 --> 00:20:19,027
I didn't take good care of Mu Ze.

230
00:20:19,107 --> 00:20:20,398
It's not your fault.

231
00:20:22,422 --> 00:20:23,761
He's an adult.

232
00:20:24,559 --> 00:20:27,967
He should be responsible
for his decision.

233
00:20:30,822 --> 00:20:31,925
Liang Ren Dong.

234
00:20:32,337 --> 00:20:34,044
You're so heartless.

235
00:20:41,682 --> 00:20:43,046
Director Song.

236
00:20:44,469 --> 00:20:46,015
Can we visit him?

237
00:20:47,512 --> 00:20:49,527
His body is very weak now.

238
00:20:49,940 --> 00:20:51,859
It's better not to enter the ward.

239
00:20:52,742 --> 00:20:53,921
I understand.

240
00:20:55,182 --> 00:20:56,748
We won't enter the ward.

241
00:20:57,168 --> 00:20:58,789
We will look from outside.

242
00:21:00,942 --> 00:21:01,944
Sure.

243
00:22:21,192 --> 00:22:22,298
Xiao Xiao.

244
00:22:23,622 --> 00:22:27,171
Did I wash my hands
before stitching the wound?

245
00:22:32,892 --> 00:22:34,008
I don't remember.

246
00:22:35,672 --> 00:22:37,535
I don't remember anything.

247
00:22:37,615 --> 00:22:39,426
Of course, you don't remember it.

248
00:22:39,506 --> 00:22:41,315
You don't have to remember it.

249
00:22:41,395 --> 00:22:44,396
It's a classical conditioning
in every surgeon.

250
00:22:44,476 --> 00:22:46,181
It's impossible that you will forget.

251
00:22:46,617 --> 00:22:47,666
Please.

252
00:22:47,746 --> 00:22:49,635
Don't be so paranoid.

253
00:22:50,135 --> 00:22:53,322
They are still checking
why he was infected.

254
00:22:53,402 --> 00:22:55,076
There is no conclusion yet.

255
00:22:55,156 --> 00:22:58,017
Why do you take responsibility for that?

256
00:22:59,062 --> 00:23:01,506
Do you want more conflicts to happen?

257
00:23:02,697 --> 00:23:03,660
I...

258
00:23:07,032 --> 00:23:08,059
Hello.

259
00:23:08,344 --> 00:23:09,501
Xia Chu.

260
00:23:09,581 --> 00:23:12,703
Director Chen wants you and Xiao Xiao
to come to the meeting room.

261
00:23:12,783 --> 00:23:13,894
Now?

262
00:23:13,974 --> 00:23:15,060
Yes.

263
00:23:25,787 --> 00:23:26,662
Sir, Xia Chu reports.

264
00:23:27,222 --> 00:23:28,314
Come in.

265
00:23:32,702 --> 00:23:34,640
Sir, are you looking for me?

266
00:23:36,039 --> 00:23:36,892
Where is Xiao Xiao?

267
00:23:36,982 --> 00:23:38,807
She was stopped by
the patient's family members.

268
00:23:38,887 --> 00:23:40,161
She will be here soon.

269
00:23:43,102 --> 00:23:44,842
Let's start.

270
00:23:47,222 --> 00:23:48,271
Recently,

271
00:23:48,771 --> 00:23:52,116
there have been
two surgical site infection cases.

272
00:23:52,504 --> 00:23:55,346
It's caused by Acinetobacter Baumannii.

273
00:23:55,426 --> 00:23:58,888
First patient, Liu Ran has passed away.

274
00:23:58,977 --> 00:24:01,269
And now, the patient is Liang Mu Ze.

275
00:24:01,349 --> 00:24:04,635
Currently, he is in the
emergency intensive care unit.

276
00:24:05,288 --> 00:24:06,652
We are not sure what will happen.

277
00:24:06,732 --> 00:24:10,089
If the first case was an accident,

278
00:24:11,462 --> 00:24:15,882
then we have to take the
second case very seriously.

279
00:24:18,622 --> 00:24:19,542
Today,

280
00:24:19,622 --> 00:24:22,362
