Xia Chu.

286
00:24:40,622 --> 00:24:41,601
You go first.

287
00:24:42,090 --> 00:24:44,239
You have dealt with both patients.

288
00:24:45,022 --> 00:24:46,881
Especially Liang Mu Ze.

289
00:24:46,961 --> 00:24:48,517
You stitched his wound.

290
00:24:49,622 --> 00:24:52,082
