304
00:25:50,942 --> 00:25:53,051
There wasn't any operational problem.

305
00:25:59,821 --> 00:26:01,089
Sir, Xiao Xiao reports.

306
00:26:01,169 --> 00:26:02,207
Come in.

307
00:26:03,822 --> 00:26:04,728
Xiao Xiao.

308
00:26:04,808 --> 00:26:06,748
You were at the site during the rescue.

309
00:26:08,597 --> 00:26:09,539
Xiao Xiao.

310
00:26:09,620 --> 00:26:12,758
