how a professional doctor...

317
00:26:29,262 --> 00:26:31,182
should be when treating a patient.

318
00:26:48,353 --> 00:26:52,841
So about the prevention
of Acinetobacter Baumannii,

319
00:26:53,622 --> 00:26:55,481
do you have any opinion?

320
00:26:55,561 --> 00:26:56,671
We can discuss.

321
00:26:56,751 --> 00:26:57,982
