324
00:27:05,804 --> 00:27:07,067
Of course, I know.

325
00:27:07,147 --> 00:27:09,178
That's why I asked if you could do it.

326
00:27:09,729 --> 00:27:10,815
You said you can.

327
00:27:10,895 --> 00:27:12,981
