that you wanted to save him.

329
00:27:17,087 --> 00:27:19,110
But you weren't calm, were you?

330
00:27:23,372 --> 00:27:24,939
I thought we were friends.

331
00:27:26,360 --> 00:27:28,489
I don't know what
your definition of a friend is.

332
00:27:29,211 --> 00:27:30,971
I treat you as my friend.

333
00:27:31,051 --> 00:27:34,503
That's why I want to tell you that
when you're facing this patient,

334
00:27:34,583 --> 00:27:37,958
you personal feelings have taken over
your professional ethics.

335
00:27:40,312 --> 00:27:43,215
When Mr Zhou asked me about my opinion,

336
00:27:43,706 --> 00:27:45,535
I voiced out my intuition.

337
00:27:47,002 --> 00:27:48,047
I didn't want to lie.

338
00:27:48,127 --> 00:27:51,003
I didn't ask you to lie.
You just had to keep quiet.

339
00:27:51,083 --> 00:27:52,730
Isn't this your forte?

340
00:27:57,374 --> 00:27:59,297
I know you want to be
the chief resident doctor.

341
00:28:00,422 --> 00:28:03,894
I never thought
that you would think that way too.

342
00:28:05,742 --> 00:28:09,223
I never thought
that you would think that way.

343
00:28:27,982 --> 00:28:29,026
Xia Chu.

344
00:28:37,942 --> 00:28:38,942
Mr Zhang.

345
00:28:40,166 --> 00:28:41,444
Are you busy now?

346
00:28:44,582 --> 00:28:47,088
It's regarding Mu Ze's medical condition.

347
00:28:49,299 --> 00:28:50,871
His condition is bad.

348
00:28:51,582 --> 00:28:53,282
I really want to save him.

349
00:28:53,362 --> 00:28:55,798
But I don't know what else I can do.

350
00:28:58,422 --> 00:29:00,402
Sir, please teach me.

351
00:29:06,312 --> 00:29:08,362
Please teach me.

352
00:29:12,802 --> 00:29:18,822
♪Whatever evidence♪

353
00:29:19,302 --> 00:29:24,542
♪Requires no validation♪

354
00:29:25,482 --> 00:29:31,672
♪It is our shared secret♪

355
00:29:31,882 --> 00:29:37,632
♪Keeping it close to the heart♪

356
00:29:37,962 --> 00:29:43,542
♪The embrace I long for♪

357
00:29:44,352 --> 00:29:49,432
♪Comes up in my dreams often♪

358
00:29:50,542 --> 00:29:56,652
♪If I hang in there♪

359
00:29:57,170 --> 00:30:03,992
♪I know love will surely come, someday♪

360
00:30:06,462 --> 00:30:07,945
Dear Professor Ye Jun.

361
00:30:08,025 --> 00:30:10,162
I apologise for contacting you
out of the blue...

362
00:30:10,242 --> 00:30:13,412
I'm a doctor from Hospital 109
of the People's Liberation Army.

363
00:30:15,079 --> 00:30:17,178
I tried calling your office phone number
but couldn't get through.

364
00:30:17,258 --> 00:30:19,216
I've sent you an SMS
but you didn't reply.

365
00:30:19,296 --> 00:30:22,127
I wonder
if you've received my previous email.

366
00:30:22,541 --> 00:30:24,832
The patient's condition
is deteriorating.

367
00:30:25,822 --> 00:30:27,963
He is starting to have septic shock.

368
00:30:28,043 --> 00:30:31,402
He is in coma and has hallucinations.

369
00:30:32,239 --> 00:30:34,631
These are signs of impending death.

370
00:30:40,782 --> 00:30:42,838
Stay calm. Let's just wait.

371
00:30:48,312 --> 00:30:49,750
