422
00:33:35,557 --> 00:33:37,630
It's not the same.

423
00:33:38,166 --> 00:33:39,551
I know he is with the special forces.

424
00:33:39,631 --> 00:33:43,250
Even though I didn't see him,
I felt ease.

425
00:33:46,142 --> 00:33:47,139
I...

426
00:33:47,219 --> 00:33:49,356
I dare not think about it.

427
00:33:49,850 --> 00:33:51,406
I dare not.

428
00:34:08,662 --> 00:34:11,874
Let's not do the phage therapy.

429
00:34:13,422 --> 00:34:14,677
It's too risky.

430
00:34:17,713 --> 00:34:18,975
Believe in him.

431
00:34:20,261 --> 00:34:22,321
He will make his own choice.

432
00:34:41,182 --> 00:34:42,135
Braised Egg.

433
