447
00:35:48,102 --> 00:35:49,202
I'm here.

448
00:35:50,032 --> 00:35:51,572
You will be fine.

449
00:35:56,742 --> 00:35:58,082
As long as we are together,

450
00:35:59,982 --> 00:36:02,202
