456
00:36:38,862 --> 00:36:39,914
If...

457
00:36:44,502 --> 00:36:46,522
you want to give it a try,

458
00:36:49,112 --> 00:36:51,092
please give me a sign.

459
00:36:53,262 --> 00:36:59,452
♪The best would be mutual affection,
having good feelings, hiding nothing♪

460
00:37:01,670 --> 00:37:07,632
♪The best would be not answering,
anticipating, avoiding misery♪

461
00:37:08,372 --> 00:37:15,028
♪Perhaps real happiness
is simple after all♪

462
00:37:18,942 --> 00:37:20,002
I got it.

463
00:37:21,542 --> 00:37:22,572
Don't worry.

464
00:37:23,902 --> 00:37:25,322
I will make sure you're safe.

465
00:37:35,822 --> 00:37:37,102
I've talked to my dad.

466
00:37:37,193 --> 00:37:39,253
He will use his network
in the medical field...

467
00:37:39,382 --> 00:37:41,522
